name: Kübra
overview: When a suburban man receives messages that seem to predict the future, he develops a following — and powerful enemies.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: With new powers — and new problems — will Gökhan lead his followers to salvation or damnation?

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Gökhan receives a mysterious text from someone named Kübra that seems to predict the future, sending him into a crisis of identity and faith.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: As Gülcan grieves their father's death, Gökhan faces the ultimate test from Kübra.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: As Gökhan's acts mystify onlookers, the police begin to investigate him. His family grapples with their place in his new life.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Merve tries to convince Gökhan to speak to the media. As his following grows, Semavi attracts the wrong kind of attention.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: As Gökhan's supporters mourn a difficult loss, tensions boil over, causing rifts in his following that lead to clashes with law enforcement.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Inspector Kara confronts Semavi over something personal. At Merve and Gökhan’s wedding, Gülcan learns a terrible secret.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Gökhan discovers the unnerving truth behind the attempt on his life. Merve faces the fallout of her actions.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Confronted with the astonishing truth behind Kübra, Gökhan must decide whether to give up on his followers or push forward.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Following a shocking feat, the government searches desperately for Gökhan and his followers. In Semavi's underground camp, cracks begin to form.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Merve learns a dangerous secret that puts everything in jeopardy. Meanwhile, Gökhan clashes with his allies about how to use their newfound influence.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Gülcan escapes with an old flame. Merve investigates a mystery of her own. Gökhan becomes increasingly isolated, even within his camp.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: A raid at the camp leads to great losses. Gökhan swears revenge as he continues his search for Gülcan.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Pushed to the brink, Gökhan escalates his movement — with dangerous consequences — and a secret relationship is revealed.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: An investigator goes rogue to get a hold of answers. Berk comes into contact with the people he helped indoctrinate.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: With just a few faithfuls left, Berk must make one last attempt to reach his goal. But before he will play along, Gökhan wants to see his sister.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: With the streets in crisis and the authorities closing in, will Gökhan finish what he started — or end it once and for all?
